{"data":[{"date":"17:26 31/07","title":"V\u00ec sao ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/vi-sao-kieu-toc-cua-pogba-o-world-cup-2018-khong-thay-doi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do anh kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7u trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Nga.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"T\u1ea1i sao anh kh\u00f4ng nhu\u1ed9m t\u00f3c \u1edf World Cup\", m\u1ed9t fan \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi cho Pogba trong cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean Instagram m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1ch t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng b\u1edfi l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3\".\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/cc-3978-1533023325.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a Pogba l\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c, theo t\u1eebng tu\u1ea7n. Anh t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c fan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\"T\u00f4i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n\", Pogba chia s\u1ebb. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0u m\u00e8, t\u1eadp trung h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh trong t\u1eebng pha b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eaft chiu m\u1ed7i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra gi\u00fap Pogba th\u0103ng hoa. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o lam.<br />\r\nAdvertisement<br />\r\n<br />\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf MU l\u00e0 Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i: \"Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Paul c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi anh \u1ea5y t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac Paul t\u1eadn hi\u1ebfn cho CLB\".<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, Pogba c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb r\u1eb1ng huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng World Cup c\u1ee7a anh \"b\u1ecb\" m\u1eb9 gi\u1eef v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i cho anh. \"Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0 \u1ea5y v\u1eabn nh\u1edb v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho t\u00f4i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 n\u00e0y\", ng\u00f4i sao MU n\u00f3i.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4890","checkdouble":"192411"},{"date":"17:32 31/07","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Italia","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/lo-dien-to-am-cua-gia-dinh-ronaldo-tai-italia.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4889","checkdouble":"192413"},{"date":"17:50 31/07","title":"Ng\u00f4i sao Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/ngoi-sao-messi-tap-luyen-voi-cho-cung-truoc-mua-giai-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, Messi \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng t\u00ean Hulk tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2>Sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, Messi \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh m\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u00f4i sao Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u00f4i sao Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/0_Lionel-Messi-even-makes-his-dog-look-stupid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ng\u00f4i sao Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111o\u1ea1n video m\u00e0 c\u00f4 v\u1ee3 Antonella Roccuzzo \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, \u201csi\u00eau sao\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u201cqu\u00e2n xanh\u201d \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng Hulk.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111o\u1ea1n clip n\u00e0y, Messi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u00e2ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i\u00eau luy\u1ec7n, khi \u0111\u00f9a ngh\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ed1ng Dogue de Bourdeaux. D\u00f9 ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u201cnhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh\u201d gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 \u00edt gi\u1edd sau khi \u0111o\u1ea1n video n\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. Trong \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ea3 m\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/messi-luyen-tap.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4888","checkdouble":"192416"},{"date":"17:56 31/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/23/higuain-dong-y-toi-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec cho Chelsea: Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ch\u01a1i cho Rossoneri d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp n\u0103m sau.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Milan</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Juventus tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i. Ch\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Giuseppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Bianconeri \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Chelsea, Milan quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 31.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Higuain nh\u01b0 khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Napoli. Tuy nhi\u00ean, The Blues mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 Olivier Giroud r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Gonzalo-Higuain-dong-y-roi-Juventus-den-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Higuain v\u00e0 Bonucci s\u1eafp ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, Milan \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1edbi Juventus. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Higuain trong 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32,1 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Milan \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Leonardo Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi Mattia Caldara di chuy\u1ec3n theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn Milan v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tin x\u1ea5u cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 tin d\u1eef v\u1edbi HLV Sarri v\u00e0 Chelsea. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia r\u1ea5t m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Higuain v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Sarri t\u1eebng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c anh t\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain\" title=\"Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/14/Nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-Juventus-2-2-Tottenham-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c thay Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Milan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Khi m\u00e0 Juventus s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Milan, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00fa \u00fd. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng trung phong l\u00e0 Olivier Giroud v\u00e0 Alvaro Morata. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Giroud \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Morata s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Community Shield v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Huddersfield. <br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-3107-172-192406.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-lewandowski-cua-bayern-172-192403.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia NHA xem Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid-172-192368.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chap-nhan-chi-65-trieu-bang-mua-pulisic-172-192340.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Dortmund</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\">Chelsea th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c, c\u00e2u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4887","checkdouble":"192414"},{"date":"12:48 31/07","title":"BLV Quang Huy: VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 do hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD v\u00ec gi\u00e1 cao, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Quang Huy cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>&quot;VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 do hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam&quot;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BLV Quang Huy VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 do hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"BLV Quang Huy VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 do hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/dt-u23-viet-nam-lai-duoc-vinh-danh-tren-bao-nuoc-ngoai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 30/7, VTV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t U23 s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 4 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la cho s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu h\u1ed3i v\u1ed1n n\u00ean nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Zing.vn: &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean. Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu. Do \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o c\u00f3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1, gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t hot&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBLV nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTC c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00eam: &quot;<o:p></o:p>T\u1eeb gi\u1edd tr\u1edf \u0111i, ta c\u1ee9 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nhanh l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u00e9p gi\u00e1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t Nam&rdquo;.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c VTV kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD, BLV Quang Huy n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;B\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n th\u1ec3 thao lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y phi\u00eau l\u01b0u. N\u1ebfu gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o s\u00e2u, s\u1ee9c h\u00fat s\u1ebd c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. S\u1ee9c h\u00fat l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean mang l\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1ee1 kh\u00f4ng may \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n thua th\u00ec nguy c\u01a1 c\u0169ng cao. Cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n th\u1ec3 thao lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi ASIAD, VTV l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 trong vi\u1ec7c mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, b\u00ean b\u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 4 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup-168-192386.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup-168-192386.html\">Sau ASIAD, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup</span><br>\r\nSau khi VTV tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup v\u00ec m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#xA;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4886","checkdouble":"192391"},{"date":"13:03 31/07","title":"U23 Uzbekistan m\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng khi sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/u23-uzbekistan-mat-cau-thu-cuc-ky-quan-trong-khi-sang-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y do b\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf CLB.</h2><h2>U23 Uzbekistan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khamdamov</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Uzbekistan m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng khi sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U23 Uzbekistan m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng khi sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/khamdamov_so_17_zecg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Khamdamov (17) kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho\u00a0Uzbekistan t\u1ea1i ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, VFF \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Uzbekistan tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Ravshan Khaydarov \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd mang t\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf U23 - Cup Vinaphone 2018, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn Indonesia b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c Asiad 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t t\u1eebng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u, Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Khaydarov c\u00f3 b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a U23 Uzbekistan l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dostonbek Khamdamov. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB Anzhi \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga. Do gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khai m\u1ea1c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD n\u00ean Khamdamov kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u00c1. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c gi\u00fap U23 Uzbekistan gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Dostonbek Khamdamov c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Uzbekistan b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Khaydarov ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam-168-192391.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam-168-192391.html\">BLV Quang Huy: VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 do hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD v\u00ec gi\u00e1 cao, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Quang Huy cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4885","checkdouble":"192392"},{"date":"13:19 31/07","title":"U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-0 U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor (KT): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-dong-timor-15h00-ngay-hom-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 U16 Campuchia 1-0, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 4-0.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P:U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM 4-0 U16 \u0110\u00d4NG TIMOR\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-4-0-U16-Dong-Timor.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lich-thi-dau-u16-viet-nam-tai-giai-u16-dong-nam-a-2018-168-192170.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/lich-thi-dau-u16-viet-nam-tai-giai-u16-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lich-thi-dau-u16-viet-nam-tai-giai-u16-dong-nam-a-2018-168-192170.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 - B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng BXH - LT\u0110 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM VS U16 \u0110\u00d4NG TIMOR</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tFek4eMra-0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n th\u1eafng U16 Campuchia 1-0, tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. Sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng A gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3, c\u00f9ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi U16 Myanmar v\u00e0 U16 Indonesia nh\u01b0ng k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor AFF Cup 2018 chi\u1ec1u nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor AFF Cup 2018 chi\u1ec1u nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Truc-tiep-U16-Viet-Nam-vs-U16-Dong-Timor-AFF-Cup-2018-chieu-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 3: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 U16 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Timor b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n song c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-03.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 7: B\u00d3NG D\u1ed8I X\u00c0 NGANG. U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam su\u00fdt m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 khi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, s\u1ed1 8 Quang Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang b\u1eadt ra.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-07.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 11: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f3t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 11 Ch\u00ed B\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ee5t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-11.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 17: U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM M\u1ede T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0.</strong> Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV\u00a0V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t c\u0169ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 12 V\u0103n Chung.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-17.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 24: Sau khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, U16 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Timor ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u00f2ng ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111e d\u1ecda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 26: M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung ra pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n do b\u1ecb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor lao v\u00e0o ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u00fang lu\u1eadt.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-26.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 30: Khung g\u1ed7 l\u1ea1i c\u1ee9u nguy cho U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor sau pha lao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly c\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-30.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 32: U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM N\u00c2NG T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0 L\u00caN 2-0.</strong> V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 v\u1eabn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u. S\u1ed1 4 \u0110\u1ee9c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00eda trong nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-32.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 36: NGUY HI\u1ec2M. </strong>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i, b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u00ecm song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft g\u1ecdn.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-36.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 40: Hi\u1ec7p 1 (do y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a U16 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 40 ph\u00fat/hi\u1ec7p) \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 d\u00e0nh cho U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV\u00a0V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p U16 Campuchia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HI\u1ec6P 2</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 42:\u00a0Ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, U16 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Timor c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha uy hi\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 44: S\u1ed1 8 Quang Tr\u01b0\u1eddng tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1ea7m xa song kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U16 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Timor.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-44.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 52: L\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, x\u00e0 ngang c\u1ee9u thua cho U16 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Timor, v\u1eabn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-52.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 55: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng trong \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U16 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Timor \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u thua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-55.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 61: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t r\u1ea5t hay nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 65: M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tung ra c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i kh\u00e1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u1edf s\u00e1t v\u1ea1ch 16m50 nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111i tr\u00fang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-65.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 70:\u00a0U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM GHI B\u00c0N TH\u1ee8 3.</strong> Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c c\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Thanh Long.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-70.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 76: B\u00c0N TH\u1ee8 4 CHO U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM.</strong> Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 12 V\u0103n Chung d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m, \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 4 cho U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/U16-Viet-Nam-phut-78.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-0 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c sau khi \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p\u00a0U16 Campuchia. Hai ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa (18h30 ng\u00e0y 2/8), U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng U16 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Nam \u00c1 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U16 Indonesia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-0 U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor (KT) Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-0 U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Timor (KT) Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/U16-Viet-Nam-4-0-U16-Dong-Timor-(KT)-Chien-thang-de-dang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Danh s\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec3n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4884","checkdouble":"192393"},{"date":"17:14 31/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Real Madrid 07h05 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-real-madrid-07h05-ngay-18-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU vs Real Madrid l\u00fac 07h05 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Real Madrid 07h05 ng\u00e0y 18 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Real Madrid 07h05 ng\u00e0y 18 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/mu-vs-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">MU vs Real Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>MU vs Real Madrid: 2-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Manchester United s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup 2018 trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9 b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Real Madrid. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1eddi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t, khi BTC gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u x\u1ebfp l\u1ecbch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng may l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a VCK World Cup 2018, nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf Man United \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn cho s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3m \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi 2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0, s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u1edd xem m\u1ed9t Jose Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00eau ca, ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. M\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1 World Cup ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u1edf M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNemanja Matic, Antonio Valencia, Eric Baily, Chris Smalling, Luke Shaw ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia l\u00e0 n\u1eb7ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi v\u1ebft \u0111au \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ea7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. Baily th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool 1-4 d\u00f9 \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111au.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111ang b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y Mourinho v\u00e0 khi \u00f4ng v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi quan, hay c\u00e0u nh\u00e0u th\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb - nh\u01b0 Andreas Pereira ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00edu k\u00e9o s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan b\u00ean trong Special One.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, Matteo Darmian l\u1ea1i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, Man United \u0111ang gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1ng l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n m\u00e0 Mourinho t\u1ea1o ra khi\u1ebfn ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o. Gareth Bale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 th\u00e1ng, Bale t\u1eebng b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi Real Madrid, d\u00f9 anh l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 X\u1ee9 Wales khi c\u1ea3 HLV Zinedine Zidane l\u1eabn Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i chia tay s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez mang v\u1ec1, Bale \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean vai tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u00e0m Madridista qu\u00ean \u0111i CR7. L\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u2013 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ec3 Bale hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a tham v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi t\u1eadp trung cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi sang M\u1ef9, gi\u1edbi quan s\u00e1t lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Bale c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ed9 ba BBC ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u2013 Karim Benzema.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, \u1edf Real Madrid c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m, trong \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c Lopetegui \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra sao cho m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m g\u00ec Bale \u2013 duy tr\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Lopetegui l\u00e0 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 tr\u1ebb m\u00e0 \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Real Madrid kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng mu\u1ed9n t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 l\u1ea1i cho ph\u00e9p \u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0110\u1ee9c, Costa Rica.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, Lopetegui s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u01b0 Vinicius Junior, Alvaro Odriozola.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 cho Los Blancos v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3ng m\u00e1y sau nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, trong khi Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn. V\u1eady n\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Lopetegui chia 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c nhau \u1edf 2 hi\u1ec7p th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 bao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n* L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n- Man United: Antonio Valencia, Nemanja Matic, Diogo  Dalot ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Eric Baily, Chris Smalling, Luke Shaw \u0111au nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a  ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n- Real Madrid: Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n- N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh trong 90 ph\u00fat, Man United kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y (h\u00f2a 3, thua 1).<br>\r\n-  \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft  Champions League, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Julen Lopetegui.<br>\r\n- 2 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i ICC (2014, 2017), Man United \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4883","checkdouble":"192407"},{"date":"17:18 31/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Roma 09h05 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-barca-vs-roma-09h05-ngay-18-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca vs Roma l\u00fac 09h05 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Roma 09h05 ng\u00e0y 18 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Roma 09h05 ng\u00e0y 18 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/barca-vs-roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca vs Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Barca vs Roma: 1-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Barcelona hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup (ICC). H\u1ed3i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Ernesto Valverde khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ICC \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd mang sang M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u00ec t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng b\u1edfi th\u1ebf m\u00e0 trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang theo nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Pique, Rakitic, Busquets, Suarez, Messi, Dembele, Coutinho, Alba, Umtiti, Y.Mina... \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u00ec ngh\u1ec9 sau khi tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Barcelona c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 Arthur Melo, Malcom v\u00e0 Lenglet. T\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp cho nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ICC v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018-19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 \u1edf ICC khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Tottenham trong 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. N\u00f3i \u0111\u00fang h\u01a1n, Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chung cu\u1ed9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Valverde v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u00e2n n\u00e3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Arthur Melo v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1ed9t Roma r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi d\u00e0n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7. Cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Tottenham 1-4 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n ICC, Giallorossi v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Valverde.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n 3 th\u00e1ng, Valverde \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn lao khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Roma c\u1ee7a Di Francesco \u1edf Champions League. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng t\u1ea1i Olympico. C\u0169ng b\u1edfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Valverde \u1edf Barca kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Di Francesco, Valverde h\u1eb3n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u0169. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham, Blaugrana c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Denis Suarez v\u00e0 Andre Gomes v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00ecnh th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb cho tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf ICC.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Roma \u0111\u00e3 chia tay 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson (t\u1edbi Liverpool) v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nainggolan (t\u1edbi Inter Milan). Nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n t\u1edbi 10 t\u00e2n binh, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Ante Coric, Justin Kluivert, Javier Pastore hay Ivan Marcano...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng b\u1ed5 sung \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Roma tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018-19. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kh\u00ed th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barcelona cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i danh...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- BARCELONA: V\u1eafng Denis Suarez, Andre Gomes (ch\u1ea5n  th\u01b0\u01a1ng), Pique, Rakitic, Busquets, Suarez, Messi, Dembele, Coutinho,  Alba, Umtiti, Y.Mina, Vermaelen (ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- ROMA: V\u1eafng Robin Olsen (ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4882","checkdouble":"192410"},{"date":"17:53 31/07","title":"C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/cdv-duc-bieu-tinh-bang-co-tho-nhi-ky-de-ung-ho-ozil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal, theo phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c C\u0110V b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5 t\u1eadp \u1edf Berlin, th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba cay \u0111\u1eafng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T sau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ozil cho r\u1eb1ng, anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd quay l\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng C\u0110V n\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n Axel Springer t\u1ea1i Berlin, gi\u01a1 cao nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m bi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef &ldquo;Ich bin Ozil&rdquo; (ti\u1ebfng \u0110\u1ee9c: T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil). Ngay c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee1i li\u1ec1m v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao &ndash; bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho l\u00e1 c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"D\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ozil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng l\u00e1 c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p nh\u1eafm th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Reinhard Grindel. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 cay \u0111\u1eafng th\u1ed1t l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng: &ldquo;V\u1edbi Grindel v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u00f4ng ta, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c khi \u0110T gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i, anh \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f3a d\u00f2ng m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo; tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd mong r\u1eb1ng phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadp c\u01b0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0o hoa n\u00e0y, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia phong tr\u00e0o \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil, ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ozi1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia phong tr\u00e0o \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil, ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ozi12.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/noi-oan-cua-mesut-ozil-dinh-kien-ve-thai-do-184-192145.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/Ozil-bi-phan-biet-chung-toc-Hai-trai-tim-va-duc-hanh-o-bong-da-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/noi-oan-cua-mesut-ozil-dinh-kien-ve-thai-do-184-192145.html\">N\u1ed7i oan c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil: \u0110\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9</span><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, n\u1ed7i oan c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u0169ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-bi-duc-ruong-bo-da-co-tho-nhi-ky-lo-172-191936.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/ozil-bi-duc-ruong-bo-da-co-tho-nhi-ky-lo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-bi-duc-ruong-bo-da-co-tho-nhi-ky-lo-172-191936.html\">Ozil b\u1ecb \u0110\u1ee9c ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf? \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 lo</span><br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng scandal g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, sau khi anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mesut-ozil-cay-dang-bo-tuyen-that-bai-cua-ca-nen-bong-da-421-191850.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/Lothar-Matthaus-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-tham-te-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mesut-ozil-cay-dang-bo-tuyen-that-bai-cua-ca-nen-bong-da-421-191850.html\">Mesut Ozil cay \u0111\u1eafng b\u1ecf tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c: Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1m ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea1nh l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4881","checkdouble":"192417"},{"date":"17:01 31/07","title":"7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/7-cau-thu-co-the-roi-barca-o-he-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Denis Suarez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, 24 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Denis Suarez kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao Sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 18 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trong \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 500 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-co-the-chia-tay-7-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Denis Suarez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, song thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Denis Suarez \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Denis Suarez n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 20 \u0111\u1ebfn 25 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n Valencia v\u00e0 Sevilla \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, 21 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca b\u1ecf ra 105 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Dortmund, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou song ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh. Sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Grizmann v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rafinha</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, 25 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRafinha kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Barca, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Inter Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rafinha\" title=\"Rafinha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/rafinha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rafinha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n gi\u1eefa Rafinha v\u00e0 Inter Milan c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ch\u1ec9 ghi 2 b\u00e0n sau 17 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, Inter \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Rafinha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca, song t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Paco Alcacer</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, 24 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaco Alcacer \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Luis Suarez, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 17 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paco Alcacer\" title=\"Paco Alcacer\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/acaser.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paco Alcacer</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Suarez \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, Barca c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay. Paco Alcacer kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u00ednh b\u00e1n anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t Paco Alcacer, Barc c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Hi\u1ec7n Valencia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Bilbao c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, 25 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ernesto Valverde s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andre Gomes\" title=\"Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/gomes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andre Gomes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Andre Gomes c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Andre Gomes</span>, Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Gomes n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Aleix Vidal<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, 28 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleix Vidal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, anh hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aleix Vidal\" title=\"Aleix Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aleix Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSergi Roberto v\u00e0 Nelson Semedo c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Aleix Vidal g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thanh l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 15 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Inter Milan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Aleix Vidal, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7, 33 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Thomas Vermaelen ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 1000 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Umtiti v\u00e0 Pique. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Vermaelen\" title=\"Thomas Vermaelen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vemar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Vermaelen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Clement Lenglet, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7, HLV Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Theo Sport, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Crystal Palace v\u00e0 Watford \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Vermaelen tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4880","checkdouble":"192405"},{"date":"16:32 31/07","title":"Tottenham nh\u1eadn b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u01a1 b\u1eafp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/tottenham-phai-mua-kondogbia-gia-70-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham ph\u1ea3i mua Kondogbia gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u01b0a ra sau bu\u1ed5i th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i theo nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Mirror.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham quan t\u00e2m Kondogbia</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Tottenham \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Victor Wanyama ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean mi\u00ean, Mousa Dembele \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 31 c\u00f2n Harry Winks thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Spurs r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Eric Dier thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Valencia v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Geoffrey Kondogbia. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Lens tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kinh qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB nh\u01b0 Sevilla, Monaco, Inter Milan v\u00e0 Valencia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham ph\u1ea3i mua Kondogbia gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham ph\u1ea3i mua Kondogbia gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Tottenham-phai-mua-Kondogbia-gia-70-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kondogbia t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Valencia m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01a1i cho Valencia d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Inter m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Kondogbia \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf trung tuy\u1ebfn, r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh trong tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Mestalla.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u1ea3i chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a 2017/18, Kondogbia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Valencia mua \u0111\u1ee9t t\u1eeb Inter. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady, c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 Tottenham ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, sau c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Valencia d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t Tottenham ph\u1ea3i mua Kondogbia gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Kondogbia\" title=\"tien ve Kondogbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/tottenham-phai-mua-kondogbia-gia-70-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham ph\u1ea3i mua Kondogbia gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Daniel Levy c\u1ee7a Spurs lu\u00f4n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh trong chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 li\u1ec7u \u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u1ec3 chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay kh\u00f4ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Valencia gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Kondogbia. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Pochettino c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o t\u1edbi s\u00e2n White Hart Lane h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-172-192372.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-172-192372.html\">V\u00ec c\u00e2u n\u00f3i n\u00e0y, Pochettino khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V Tottenham lo ngay ng\u00e1y</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham. \u00d4ng th\u00fa nh\u1eadn CLB th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish-172-192258.html\">Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua sao h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-ra-dieu-kien-mua-alderweireld-cho-mu-172-192150.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Tottenham, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-tottenham-va-mu-trao-doi-bom-tan-172-191994.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Tottenham v\u00e0 MU trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-tai-ngo-modric-172-191894.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Modric</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4879","checkdouble":"192400"},{"date":"16:43 31/07","title":"Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/antonio-conte-hai-nam-nem-trai-du-hi-no-ai-o-cung-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec7m k\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Mourinho, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Mourinho, Scolari, Villas-Boas v\u00e0 Conte. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1eddi Chelsea theo m\u1ed9t \u201ck\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n\u201d ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n gi\u1ed1ng nhau: t\u1eeb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Wembley t\u1ed1i 19/5, Chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap FA, Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Manchester United 1-0 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11m c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, v\u1edbi n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi t\u01b0\u01a1i r\u00f3i khi n\u00e2ng cao danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 2 \u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Chelsea, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues.</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte: Hai nam nem trai du Hi No Ai O cung Chelsea1\" title=\"Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/co.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y 13/7, t\u1ee9c 25 ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng Chelsea v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA, Conte ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb&nbsp; BL\u0110 The Blues sa th\u1ea3i, k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1eafc m\u00e0u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Gi\u1edd Conte \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ean l\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Gi\u1edd The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh HLV m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00e1c - Maurizio Sarri. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, c\u00e1c True Blues s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn k\u00ed \u1ee9c n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 Conte?&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t Conte h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch? M\u1ed9t Conte t\u00e0i ba h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh 3-4-3 (c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn chu\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2016/17? M\u1ed9t Conte &ldquo;\u0111\u1ed9c t\u00e0i&rdquo; qua tin nh\u1eafn&hellip; y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Diego Costa t\u00ecm CLB kh\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t Conte sa l\u1ea7y trong cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ea9u chi\u1ebfn cay nghi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Stamford Bridge &ndash; Jose Mourinho. Hay m\u1ed9t Conte c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed9c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Conte trong tim c\u00e1c C\u0110V Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u00e0&hellip; Conte n\u00e0o th\u00ec n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh: Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia hay chia tay \u00f4ng, h\u1eb3n \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c True Bules s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn v\u1ebf th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t. B\u1edfi h\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea th\u1eddi Roman Abramovich ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Conte \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt &ldquo;Conte&rdquo; nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 sau Conte ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u &ldquo;Conte&rdquo; n\u1eefa. S\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf HLV \u1edf Stamford Bridge l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 xa x\u1ec9!<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa thai HLV Antonio Conte truoc them mua giai moi.\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Thuc-hu-chuyen-Antonio-Conte-dan-dat-AC-Milan-thay-Gattuso-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau Conte, Sarri l\u00e0 HLV th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong v\u00f2ng 5 n\u0103m qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 12 l\u01b0\u1ee3t HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft The Blues trong tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0 Ray Wilkins hay Steve Holland. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng hay vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 Chelsea s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1ec3 chia tay HLV m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng &ldquo;tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0 Conte!<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1ec1 n\u1ed5i. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00e2u xa lu\u00f4n b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng &ndash; m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa HLV Chelsea v\u00e0 Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB. T\u1ec9 ph\u00fa Abramovich l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Chelsea th\u1eddi hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, bi\u1ebfn The Blues t\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 l\u00e0 1 CLB h\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 90 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh 1 trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1eeb 2003. Nh\u01b0ng Abramovich c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 v\u0103n h\u00f3a d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t Stamford Bridge khi\u1ebfn The Blues kh\u00e1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh nh\u01b0 United, Liverpool hay Arsenal. M\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 v\u0103n h\u00f3a coi HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m thu\u00ea cho Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec7m k\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Mourinho, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Mourinho, Scolari, Villas-Boas v\u00e0 Conte. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1eddi Chelsea theo m\u1ed9t &ldquo;k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n gi\u1ed1ng nhau: t\u1eeb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" title=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea thay Conte b\u1eb1ng HLV Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u00f3 t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec1 &ldquo;C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ph\u00eda sau \u0110\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 V\u1ef1c s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Conte \u1edf Chelsea&rdquo; \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean Express h\u00f4m 13/6 &ndash; \u0111\u00fang 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Simon Johnson vi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00e1ch v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00e1c \u0111a s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Anh. Conte bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y H\u00e8 2016. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau khi gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u0103ng quang Premier Laegue 2016/17 trong ho\u00e0nh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb CLB \u1edf c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Conte tin r\u1eb1ng gi\u1edd \u00f4ng ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Conte \u0111\u00e3 sai. Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Conte v\u1edbi BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. Conte th\u1ef1c ra \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1ec9 1 th\u00e1ng sau khi \u0111\u01b0a Chelsea l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&rdquo;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ph\u1ea3n th\u1ea7y&rdquo;, &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 gh\u1ebf HLV&rdquo;, ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i khi Chelsea c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e2m nguy, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf c\u00e1c fan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb ng\u1eef nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 The Blues. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 th\u1eadt, ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u1ed1 1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tri\u1ec7u ph\u00fa c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00e0 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7t HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00f3m c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p. Nh\u01b0 bao \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Conte c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u1ea5y trong h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte trong tran Chelsea 1-0 MU chung ket FA Cup 2017/18\" title=\"Antonio Conte trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 MU chung k\u1ebft FA Cup 2017/18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Zinedine-Zidane-tu-chuc-HLV-truong-cua-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Antonio Conte trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 MU chung k\u1ebft FA Cup 2017/18</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Costa ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Conte kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi sau v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m &ldquo;tin nh\u1eafn cho ngh\u1ec9&rdquo; h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, Willian d\u00f9ng c\u00fap che m\u1eb7t Conte trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. Courtois, trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Sarri gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6 d\u00f9 Conte&ndash; tr\u00ean danh ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf - v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u00f3m d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Mario Balotelli hay Hatem Ben Arfa, m\u1ea5y khi d\u00e1m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00f3ng Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB? \u0110\u1eddi Conte c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady tr\u00ean t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t HLV, t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb thu\u00ea \u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay Conte \u0111\u00f3n sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 49 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i r\u1ea5t xa Chelsea, sau 2 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7y b\u00e3o t\u00e1p \u1edf Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t Sarri \u1edf v\u00e0o ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 Conte hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i? Hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng bi \u0111\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>ELFLACO (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4878","checkdouble":"192401"}]}